snippet.title: The Office
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official channel for The Office U.S.  Follow the daily pranks, office romances and all the drama that plagues the 9-to-5 world in this 'docu-reality' of modern American office life.  

Streaming now on Peacock: www.peacocktv.com

Watch exclusive interviews, mashups and comedy gems from our very own Steve Carell, Jenna Fischer, Rainn Wilson and many more famous faces.  Subscribe now: http://bit.ly/subOfficeUS.

HILARIOUS videos from The Office US uploaded Monday, Wednesday and Saturday, so make sure to subscribe so you don't miss a thing http://bit.ly/subOfficeUS
